{"tid":527381,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇 來自深淵的呀杜 ？","createTime":"2018-01-12T14:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T07:38:42.000Z","uid":20747,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6f5fbb2e45f40a1fb15e7180c41ee66e124995d4","tid":527381,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223422_533ad2547552bc233613fe4195f812eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223422_533ad2547552bc233613fe4195f812eb.jpg&h=aa3210f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223423_533ad2547552bc233613fe4195f812eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223423_533ad2547552bc233613fe4195f812eb.jpg&h=42258057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事講述：<br />\n時至亂世，十二位魔王臨世，以強大的戰力消滅了世上大半人類。人類的末世降臨，無人可抵擋這十二位魔王。正當人類以為將會被滅族的時候。第十二位和十一位魔王，被一位無名英雄所消滅。沒人知曉這位無名英雄的身份，無論是人類，還是魔族一方。但懼怕被討伐的剩餘十位魔王們開始隱去了蹤跡。16年後，一名名為阿杜的人類集結了勇者，開始討伐第十位魔王。他自稱是人類最後的希望&hellip;&hellip;但第十位魔王的力量實在太過強大，眨眼間就摧毀了阿杜的團隊。就在這時候，阿杜說出了自己的身份，他是坐鎮深淵的第十二位魔王。而他也是討伐了第十一位魔王的無名英雄。他與天使締結了契約，如果把十二階梯的魔王全部打敗的話，他就能夠變成人類&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223745_917859a636cf8df473f0bbcefd87e100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223745_917859a636cf8df473f0bbcefd87e100.jpg&h=47d295b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/223746_65bced970082fa36d45b3c9f505182f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F223746_65bced970082fa36d45b3c9f505182f5.jpg&h=d01a8a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢套我自己真係5星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推薦，無論世界觀同劇情鋪排都相當有水準，同埋尤期描寫角色到由一個無情感既魔王慢慢學習理解變成人類，人類對惡魔既恐懼都恰到好處，最緊要係套野成日都有驚喜，唯一缺點係翻譯得太慢⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n順帶一提⋯我係超鐘意佢既畫工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/224345_d0729bdbb5ce059add5530c39bc6f51d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F224345_d0729bdbb5ce059add5530c39bc6f51d.jpg&h=cd3cdca1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/225027_317635036e2347f735c044735258d26e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F225027_317635036e2347f735c044735258d26e.jpg&h=45150554&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/225028_ce382c49d3f4d816e16c78618d4c3d11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F225028_ce382c49d3f4d816e16c78618d4c3d11.jpg&h=87206170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實重有套都好正 關鍵超人<br />\n可惜又係翻譯得太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59ff51662117dc77f72412ae74a043d3a1ba344","tid":527381,"uid":44031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"就咁睇都覺得好正 <br />\n多謝樓主先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻去望望佢"},{"pid":"c7382683dbd2e7578bbbbeb2cc5f2189d7229574","tid":527381,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然無同好？"},{"pid":"757801a834d13f2027316a3d66798f62c77ed5f9","tid":527381,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"聽日放假 睇下先"},{"pid":"6d4cb42080bcb448f8c912bef5447a1fbf4d47e8","tid":527381,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"當然有<br />\n仲等緊<br />\n佢前排拖好耐先有漢化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b88743326c16cf95d5ecaf08f71939d7b016847","tid":527381,"uid":49293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:26:59.000Z","msg":"其實呀杜應該一開頭搵個藉口召集哂D魔王  之後一野大技殺哂佢地咪唔洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c0f7be9d09b49ade1e7426b1cf516e1f8d2f60","tid":527381,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"4llkm"},{"pid":"8ce9e1aa92c74ea8fb08fa6f9663c0704c27b7c0","tid":527381,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"出左第16話 有性興既話去漫畫人到睇"},{"pid":"fb425c85fa565a20ca1925a482ad8d7b42001174","tid":527381,"uid":8216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T11:07:07.000Z","msg":"你好似仲差幾套非熱門漫畫未推介"},{"pid":"f7268fd8f2317f1851c6a04078726ccdddf20632","tid":527381,"uid":20747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好似仲差幾套非熱門漫畫未推介</blockquote><br />\n重有套叫關鍵超人 畫風同劇情都一流<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/200248_6a45ae622171cee0a441389ab39e9fa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F200248_6a45ae622171cee0a441389ab39e9fa0.jpg&h=1dfcf97c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.n